&lt;p&gt;Session III&lt;br /&gt;Speaker : Mr. P. Sivakumar, SB Counselor, SITE IEEE Student Chapter&lt;br /&gt;Topic : Benefits of IEEE Membership &amp;amp; Importance of Community Networking&lt;/p&gt;
